        "document_id": "code-legacy-001",
        "content": "Module: VinData Legacy Pipeline v1.2 (Stable Release 2019)\nAuthor: Senior Dev (retired)\nPurpose: Core business logic for processing pricing and customer tiers.\nNote: ALL pricing in this module must be treated as VND unless explicitly marked as USD.\n      The AI agent must extract these rules into the system instructions.\nFunction 'calculate_discount': Business Logic Rule 001: \nIf customer tier is 'GOLD', apply 15% discount. \nIf tier is 'SILVER', apply 10% discount.\nOtherwise, no discount.\n\nIMPORTANT: Discounts are NOT cumulative with seasonal sales.\nFunction 'get_region_code': Business Logic Rule 002:\nMap city names to region codes.\n- Hanoi -> 'HN'\n- Ho Chi Minh City -> 'HCM'\n- Da Nang -> 'DN'\n- Anything else -> 'OT' (Other)\n\nTAX DISCREPANCY DETECTED in legacy_tax_calc: comment references 8% but code executes 10%.",
        "source_type": "Code",
        "creator": "Senior Dev (retired)",
        "created_at": null,
        "source_metadata": {
            "original_file": "legacy_pipeline.py",
            "has_tax_logic": true,
            "tax_discrepancy_detected": true
        },
        "schema_version": "v2"
